  "text": "Zhang et al. modified the ionic liquids to CdSe/ZnS QDs based on electrostatic interaction, interacted with carbaryl and methacrylic acid, deposited a MIP on the surface of CdSe/ZnS QDs, and finally obtained molecularly imprinted quantum dot fluorescent probes. The linear range of carbaryl was 0.0398-49.7 μM, and the detection limit was 14.7 nM [CITATION_1] . Ren ",
